A program to help review and memorize Russian (or any language) words.
I will be updating it from time to time with Russian vocabulary words.

To use:

1) Download the source.
2) type: make
3) type: make run

If you don't have a database, one will be created.
Relies on SQLite.
Only tested on OSX, if you find errors on other platforms, please let me know.

